graph TB
    subgraph "Consistent Hashing Ring"
        direction TB
        N1((Node A)) ---|hash range| N2((Node B))
        N2 ---|hash range| N3((Node C))
        N3 ---|hash range| N1
    end

    K1[Key 1] -.->|maps to| N1
    K2[Key 2] -.->|maps to| N2
    K3[Key 3] -.->|maps to| N3

    Note[Adding/removing a node<br/>only affects adjacent keys]
